Car and General Trading Limited launched a TVS motorcycle promotion, 'TVS Chomoka na Gari', which will run for eight weeks until February 18. This campaign will reward a lucky TVS buyer with a Grand Prize of a Toyota Vitz. There will also be TVS HLX 100X motorcycles which will be awarded monthly and 32 inch Samsung TVs and subwoofers up for grabs on a weekly basis. The competition will be divided into eight regions: Nairobi, Mt Kenya, Nyanza, Upper Rift, Lower Rift, Coast, Western and Eastern.